<ab facs="#facs_28_r2l6">den <expan>halbwachſ<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> ʒu rede geſecʒt <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> . Der hat vns <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> </ab>
